init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mugs were made by a company called "Mugs R Us" and were made to be a fun little gift to give to dads

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mugs were shipped out to every dad in the world and when they were turned on, they showed the ranking of the dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Some dads were so upset that they committed suicide.
